body_html:
I faced the same issue, solved it by changing my app/build.gradle file.

The change is simple,
Replace
compile 'org.tensorflow:tensorflow-lite:+'
With
compile 'org.tensorflow:tensorflow-lite:0.1.7'

I hope this helps.

body:
I faced the same issue, solved it by changing my app/build.gradle file.

The change is simple,
Replace
`compile 'org.tensorflow:tensorflow-lite:+'`
With 
`compile 'org.tensorflow:tensorflow-lite:0.1.7'`

I hope this helps.
